ndce_statement: Tuvalu commits to the reducing its GHG emissions from the power sector by 100% by 2030. ndce_status_2020_label: Submitted New or Updated NDC with Reduced Total Emissions
ndce_statement: Uruguay commits unconditionally to not exceed 9,267 Gg of CO2 emissions, 818 Gg of methane emissions, and 32 Gg of N2O emissions by 2035, and to reduce HFC emissions by 30% relative to BAU by 2035.
